Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:02:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.37,0:00:20.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:23.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.00,0:00:29.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.09,0:00:40.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.51,0:00:44.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.10,0:00:49.65,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:55.78,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:01:02.58,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:07.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:09.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:16.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.43,0:01:26.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:30.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.40,0:01:35.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:42.12,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, \Nlet's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.12,0:01:48.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.87,0:01:53.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.42,0:01:55.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:02:00.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.01,0:02:03.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:06.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:08.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.10,0:02:09.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:13.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.07,0:02:14.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:15.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:19.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:26.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:28.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.71,0:02:33.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.09,0:02:35.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:39.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.76,0:02:42.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.84,0:02:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.13,0:02:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.89,0:02:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.97,0:02:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.27,0:03:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.48,0:03:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered \Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the hold-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you going to kick my \Nbutt as many times as it takes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.77,0:03:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I will in just a sec, so hang tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't mind the wait,\Nbut he'll come back if you don't hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"He"? Who are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.67,0:03:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I don't have\Ntime to be goofing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to hurry back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, jeez. You're such a handful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.30,0:04:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't! Robin is a lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lady...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:12.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What of it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable! Sanji actually kicked...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Golden...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pound!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep till dawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't that samurai just say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long story short, what just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.57,0:05:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, the fight is apparently over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen a duel like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.79,0:05:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That samurai wasn't taking me\Nthe least bit seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Slashes Dancing on the Rooftop!!\NShowdown: Zoro vs. Ryuma!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that you can steal\Nmy black sword, Shusui?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be precise, I'm going to take\Nthe sword from beside your corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You are full of spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't provoke him if I were you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you also carry three swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but one is a broken blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just carry it at my waist because\Nit doesn't feel right without it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Three-Sword Style swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Three-Sword Style swordsman?\NI've never heard of such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a circus act?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pity I can't let you\Nsee it in action right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd break that squat nose of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure. You seem quite strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Emotions beyond my \Nrecollection are surfacing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel as though I am standing\Nface to face with a giant beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.45,0:07:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a strange, exhilarating sensation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel as though I could start dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.06,0:07:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aubade Coup Droit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-He used a pistol?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It was a thrust!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.78,0:07:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I used that move,\Nit wouldn't be as impressive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He shot a hole through the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.17,0:08:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To shoot a thrust like that...\NJust how strong is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say it's a draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You nearly got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did that\NHaramaki freak get in a counter attack?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The attacks... were nearly simultaneous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he can throw his attacks as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The skirmish between them\Njust now truly did end in a draw.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The samurai zombie is currently\Nusing my shadow to move,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the samurai was probably an expert\Nswordsman when he was still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe those two may possess\Nthe same type of build as swordsmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.55,0:08:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it mean anything if\Nthey share the same build?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It means their strengths \Nlie in the same areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt this duel will last long.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prelude Au Fer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sword-breaker assault?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.99,0:09:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two-Sword Style... Flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Demon Magma Bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gavotte Bond en Avant!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two-Sword Style Sword Draw...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rashomon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.62,0:10:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He blocked my attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They slashed through the support beams!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crud! This floor is toast!\NIt's dangerous up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, hang on! We're gettin' outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole roof's comin' down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seventy-two Pound Phoenix!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Polka Remise!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weapons Left!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dang, that was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.04,0:11:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Careful! You don't want to fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.53,0:12:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Falling...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.76,0:12:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can they fight with such poor footing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid my swords will break\Nif this drags out much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He truly has the body and \Nspirit needed to support the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,strength of a legendary swordsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.21,0:13:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One-Sword Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soaring Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-Pace Hum...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Notch Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Blaze!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.67,0:14:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wound is bursting into flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once, a legendary samurai\Nwielded the great sword Shusui.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sure this katana would be\Nhappy to have you as its master.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't that samurai just say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.48,0:15:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long story short, what just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:31.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, the fight is apparently over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.11,0:15:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen a duel like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That samurai wasn't taking\Nme the least bit seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:16:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Skeleton! What do you mean it's "over"?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.19,0:16:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an incredible duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.46,0:16:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It pains my samurai heart\Nthat I must taste defeat...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you feel ashamed proves...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that you are a swordsman\Nin both mind and body!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish we could have met\Nwhen you were still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:16:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Isn't that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is! It's my shadow, \Nwhich Moria snatched away
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from me five years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! It's copying whatever I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that a given? It's your shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.05,0:17:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This might be hard for you to understand,\Nbut I'm finally my old self again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm touched! I'm moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.02,0:17:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These emotions are coursing through my veins!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, not that I have any veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.35,0:17:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they go "bone deep."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.94,0:17:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's back! After five years,\NI have a shadow again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take your sword, but I'll pretend\Nthat our duel never happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.37,0:17:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...samurai of the Wano Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Sanji has already\Nfound and rescued Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And how are Luffy and the others doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, I've just gotta tell\Neveryone about how I beat
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that Horo-Horo Chick when they\Ndidn't stand a chance against her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see their faces!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perona-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.99,0:18:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think she's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.62,0:18:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Captain Kumacy and Lieutenant\NGentleman Hippopotamus went after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.21,0:18:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By now, Mr. Negative Nose\Nis the one crying like a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew, that was a close call!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.68,0:18:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of my hard work would go down\Nthe drain if I got taken down now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There'd go my bragging rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moving on! Sanji! Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.90,0:19:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't they supposed to be\Nattending Absalom-sama's wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Special Zombie did this to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absalom-sama ordered them\Nto forcibly stop Oars,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he took them out in the blink of an eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absurd! Even though he's a\NSpecial Zombie, he's still a zombie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would he attack his comrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.72,0:19:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oars is rather new to his life as a zombie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently he still has \NStraw Hat's personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.31,0:19:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! This is a ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All righty! With this ship,\NI'm gonna become King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm not made of rubber.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.24,0:19:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.09,0:20:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in the way of my adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suspect it will take a while for him\Nto become an obedient zombie...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.60,0:20:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?! He took out all of these\NGeneral Zombies in an instant?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.11,0:20:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must have let their guard down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.03,0:20:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NOtherwise this never would have happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were you, I'd start running!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, Oars will do you in as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silence, Hildon! Are you mocking us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.82,0:20:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The monster! How dare he kill our comrades?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Absalom-sama gave those orders,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no one will mind if we \Nteach him a thing or two!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear by our title as the strongest
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that we will let Oars know just how\Npowerful the General Zombies are!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ch-Charge!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.55,0:21:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.90,0:21:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, oops! That's right. I'd forgotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to hurry on back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.00,0:22:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to all of that\Nfire you had earlier, Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Don't act so high-and-mighty
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.03,0:22:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwhen you aren't fighting, Giant Shallot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.51,0:22:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already told you:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.06,0:22:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the man who will let others\Nmake me the King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.40,0:22:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it looks like the day I realize my\Ndream has gotten a whole lot closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.78,0:22:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep taking you down until\NI recover all of the shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, defeating me won't--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.70,0:22:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When ya get down to it, I just need\Nto defeat you and this shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.59,0:22:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:23:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what happens to you,\Nbut as things stand, your future looks bleak.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.61,0:23:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A more powerful foe will be here\Nany minute now, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.30,0:23:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Chopper, listen. The zombies are happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.17,0:23:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, they are given a second\Nchance to live amongst us as humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.55,0:23:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're wrong!\N--I'm wrong? Like your medical knowhow--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.47,0:23:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! That isn't a medical procedure!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.02,0:23:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.56,0:23:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.98,0:23:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Chopper Is Furious!!\NHogback's Evil Medical Practices!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.07,0:23:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.15,0:23:49.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
